# Dependencies
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Environment variables
# Deny every .env* file by default; explicitly allow .env.example through.
# This closes a gap where .env.consciousness (and any future ad-hoc
# .env.<word>) slipped past a stricter literal-name rule.
.env*
!.env.example

